title: Dylan Thomas - Collected Works
description:
This torrent includes prose and poetry read by Dylan Thomas, as well as the 1963 radio dramatization by BBC Radio, with Richard Burton as the narrator, and the 2003 release celebrating the 50th anniversary of Dylan Thomas' death, produced by Sir George Martin with Anthony Hopkins as First Voice.


01 A Child's Christmas In Wales
02 Quite Early One Morning
03 Reminiscences Of Childhood
04 Holiday Memory
05 A Visit To Grandpa's
06 Ballad Of The Long-legged Bait
07 A Winter's Tale
08 Fern Hill
09 Poem On His Birthday
10 In The White Giant's Thigh
11 Do Not Go Gentle Into That Good Night
12 Should Lanterns Shine
13 Ceremony After A Fire Raid
14 If I Were Tickled By The Rub Of Love
15 Lament
16 There Was A Saviour
17 And Death Shall Have No Dominion
18 A Refusal To Mourn The Death, By Fire, Of A Child In London
19 Under Milk Wood (1963)
20 Under Milk Wood (2003)
